               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>The Contract shall facilitate the Reactivation work required in order to bring 13 x M3 Amphibious Rigs back in to service, whilst also providing In-Service Support to the existing In-Service M3 Rigs and the remaining 13 x M3 Rigs once reactivated to full service capability.</P>
