               <INFO_ADD>
                  <P>The Authority are committed to ensuring all Contractors working with the Dept have the required level of Cyber Security Controls. The Contract will include DEFCON658 Cyber and will follow the Defence Cyber Protection Partnership Cyber Security Model. The Contract has been classified as a Very Low Risk Level, therefore the Contractor will require Security Controls Appropriate to this level.</P>
